{"tid":34042,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"物理JJ可唔可以幫下小妹","createTime":"2016-12-11T08:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T09:53:39.000Z","uid":248,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50b8f04f38848b8b02a7caf9198bf0f267fdf539","tid":34042,"uid":248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:38:07.000Z","msg":"幾時用V^2/R同埋I^2R<br />\n做題目成日調轉用之後做錯<br />\n<br />\n利申dse雞"},{"pid":"ddfaf6829366ac6a80947378c91ff2c4453ebb40","tid":34042,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:39:45.000Z","msg":"幾時都用得"},{"pid":"d18dad9faa0a27ceece128426b93911926dd2316","tid":34042,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:41:01.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9206f84957e9a55866cac3b95f7a9e852dcd730b","tid":34042,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:41:41.000Z","msg":"power loss = I^2R<br />\npower output = V^2/R"},{"pid":"94e5c6f175c4481b9aa38537426d1df8c81bc341","tid":34042,"uid":248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:42:14.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解有時用V^2/R果陣佢要我用I^2R<br />\n係咪有d情況下唔知V係幾多果陣唔用得？"},{"pid":"ad36917a5b5a14d6476e65cde453eae6706cdfa0","tid":34042,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:42:20.000Z","msg":"點樣會計到唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9134eddff27a8305cbf206e9c98b9e851b9b473","tid":34042,"uid":248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28N6r6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28N6r6Y.jpg&h=be0feb22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用I^2R做到Ans b<br />\n但V^2/R 做到Ans d<br />\n我點知幾時用邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f102a342f98208f008587b0b331d90852f05495","tid":34042,"uid":12866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:46:24.000Z","msg":"唔熟嘅通常會搞錯個V<br />\n所以有得揀優先用I^2R<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7575ae688c5d1e638267bd8a43b5c05fffeeebbe","tid":34042,"uid":248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔熟嘅通常會搞錯個V<br />\n所以有得揀優先用I^2R<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 點分要用邊一個V"},{"pid":"a03f2c8e9528455df12eb795764fbcc1badb93db","tid":34042,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:51:00.000Z","msg":"印象中最多人錯係電塔傳電果課<br />\n以為電塔個V可以代入條式 然後個V成幾萬咁放入條式度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336faf597de63e7d410f3c69436583d75c7ccb43","tid":34042,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:51:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28N6r6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28N6r6Y.jpg&h=be0feb22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用I^2R做到Ans b<br />\n但V^2/R 做到Ans d<br />\n我點知幾時用邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢題問 total power 成個circuit 計 V 係 constant<br />\n<br />\n用 V&sup2;/R"},{"pid":"b66f2494b1c757d1cd38057bf679e15066ce2cd6","tid":34042,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔熟嘅通常會搞錯個V<br />\n所以有得揀優先用I^2R<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 點分要用邊一個V</blockquote><br />\npotential difference"},{"pid":"41f0797e053abf77974762d6013693fd34294466","tid":34042,"uid":248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:52:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印象中最多人錯係電塔傳電果課<br />\n以為電塔個V可以代入條式 然後個V成幾萬咁放入條式度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁正確要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763d0f7001f7514671b90584f0099d480ea5e2d5","tid":34042,"uid":248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:53:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28N6r6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28N6r6Y.jpg&h=be0feb22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用I^2R做到Ans b<br />\n但V^2/R 做到Ans d<br />\n我點知幾時用邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢題問 total power 成個circuit 計 V 係 constant<br />\n<br />\n用 V&sup2;/R</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係要睇邊個係constant之後就用嗰個嚟做？"},{"pid":"1e6429adbe36121159143e0f809e38cf3b850ffd","tid":34042,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:54:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28N6r6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28N6r6Y.jpg&h=be0feb22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用I^2R做到Ans b<br />\n但V^2/R 做到Ans d<br />\n我點知幾時用邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢題問 total power 成個circuit 計 V 係 constant<br />\n<br />\n用 V&sup2;/R</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係要睇邊個係constant之後就用嗰個嚟做？</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n<br />\n你果條一拍個switch，I R(equivalent) 會一齊變"},{"pid":"5c0a3c566d9bf966a76af94e19215754879cfba9","tid":34042,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:55:07.000Z","msg":"我估你係分子分母搞亂咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c1ed7d7d77015a6e31a6d36b9bf87cd87a039b","tid":34042,"uid":248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v0ccVuU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv0ccVuU.jpg&h=c56862f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有呢條 <br />\nconcept好唔清<br />\n一眼望落去我會用V^2/R=60W嚟搵個R,錯到七彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實際上我見到呢D要點諗 可唔可以解釋下我搵到嗰個800幾R係乜嘢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a02ccf1a7bcb8c941697ed6a170becfdbaa9b9","tid":34042,"uid":19162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"好似電塔為例，你用電塔個voltage output去計power loss in cable會錯係因為<br />\nPower loss in cable = (potential diff across cable)^2/cable resistance<br />\n電塔個voltage output根本唔等於Potential diff across cable，所以咪錯"},{"pid":"6b880d2063c6a64416171e4ae3dd8bce0d239407","tid":34042,"uid":248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢題問 total power 成個circuit 計 V 係 constant<br />\n<br />\n用 V&sup2;/R</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係要睇邊個係constant之後就用嗰個嚟做？</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n<br />\n你果條一拍個switch，I R(equivalent) 會一齊變</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但假如我呢條數有實數呢？有V係咪可以搵返I 再用I^2R"},{"pid":"2a911ec99b9511c4401f02e3cc4781d74d7167b2","tid":34042,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:59:25.000Z","msg":"因為個circuit close左嘅時候 V=IR R細左 I就會大左<br />\n用I^2R = P 就要用新嗰個I 計先會計到答案<br />\n所以用V^2/R 計會方便D 因為V由頭到尾都不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:18DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223714364f662346be7a7031b600788c8ed79a82","tid":34042,"uid":248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似電塔為例，你用電塔個voltage output去計power loss in cable會錯係因為<br />\nPower loss in cable = (potential diff across cable)^2/cable resistance<br />\n電塔個voltage output根本唔等於Potential diff across cable，所以咪錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2481cbec5b179ec9cbeed90818aa5735d4923b92","tid":34042,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v0ccVuU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv0ccVuU.jpg&h=c56862f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有呢條 <br />\nconcept好唔清<br />\n一眼望落去我會用V^2/R=60W嚟搵個R,錯到七彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實際上我見到呢D要點諗 可唔可以解釋下我搵到嗰個800幾R係乜嘢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條式冇錯，你記得要用 rated value 計 R<br />\n即 220&sup2;/R = 60<br />\n<br />\n呢個 R 係件電器 overall resistance, 同一件電器唔會變（除非入面有隱藏 switch 轉 mode 之類）<br />\n<br />\n而後面先用 110&sup2;/(上面答案) = 實際 power<br />\n<br />\n唔好撈亂"},{"pid":"8004f823306a583745106d94b878e16898cbd3c5","tid":34042,"uid":19162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v0ccVuU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv0ccVuU.jpg&h=c56862f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有呢條 <br />\nconcept好唔清<br />\n一眼望落去我會用V^2/R=60W嚟搵個R,錯到七彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實際上我見到呢D要點諗 可唔可以解釋下我搵到嗰個800幾R係乜嘢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLamp既resistance唔會變，所以用佢個rating 220V先搵resistance先<br />\n之後再諗將lamp放係110V既circuit度既power會係幾多"},{"pid":"c038b26f5a639a6049366099d5d22e384323bdb0","tid":34042,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:02:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v0ccVuU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv0ccVuU.jpg&h=c56862f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有呢條 <br />\nconcept好唔清<br />\n一眼望落去我會用V^2/R=60W嚟搵個R,錯到七彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實際上我見到呢D要點諗 可唔可以解釋下我搵到嗰個800幾R係乜嘢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nR = V^2 / P = 220^2/60<br />\nP = V^2 / R = 110^2 / (220^2/60) = 15<br />\nANS:A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f85413eb2f5ad7864881c78ea7c6741644cf6f","tid":34042,"uid":248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:04:13.000Z","msg":"LIHKG嘅巴打回覆真係又快又高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}